name: mm8
age_comments: Age range based on U-Pb zircon dates and Ar-Ar dates. Note: two U-Pb zircon dates yielded ages of ~46 whereas Ar-Ar ages are mostly ~10 Myrs younger (it is not clear why this is, although Miggins (2009) suggets may be due to younger [undated] intrusions). Here taking the range of ages until this is better clarified.
